# ICC T20 WC 2026 Predictor — Project Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A complete foundation for the hackathon project at `C:\Users\mmmon\.gemini\antigravity\scratch\icc-t20-wc-predictor\`.

### Dataset Strategy (Your Key Question)

| Decision | Recommendation |
|----------|---------------|
| **Primary dataset** | `t20s_male_json.zip` — ALL Men's T20 Internationals (~1,200+ matches) |
| **Use league data?** | ✅ YES — IPL/BBL/CPL data enriches player profiles and form features |
| **Player linking** | Cricsheet People Register (`people.csv`) maps player IDs across all datasets |
| **Competitive edge** | Frame as "Multi-Source T20 Intelligence System" — leagues for features, T20I for predictions |

### Files Created (17 files)

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| [settings.py](file:///C:/Users/mmmon/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/icc-t20-wc-predictor/config/settings.py) | Central config: paths, URLs, constants |
| [download_data.py](file:///C:/Users/mmmon/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/icc-t20-wc-predictor/src/ingestion/download_data.py) | Downloads & extracts Cricsheet datasets |
| [parse_cricsheet.py](file:///C:/Users/mmmon/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/icc-t20-wc-predictor/src/ingestion/parse_cricsheet.py) | JSON parser → Polars DataFrames (ball-by-ball + match info + registry) |
| [schema.py](file:///C:/Users/mmmon/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/icc-t20-wc-predictor/src/warehouse/schema.py) | DuckDB Star Schema: 5 dim + 4 fact tables across Bronze/Silver/Gold |
| [run_pipeline.py](file:///C:/Users/mmmon/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/icc-t20-wc-predictor/src/etl/run_pipeline.py) | Full ETL: Bronze→Silver→Gold with cleaning, enrichment, aggregation |
| [stream_simulator.py](file:///C:/Users/mmmon/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/icc-t20-wc-predictor/src/simulation/stream_simulator.py) | Ball-by-ball streaming (console/CSV/Kafka modes) |
| [docker-compose.yml](file:///C:/Users/mmmon/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/icc-t20-wc-predictor/docker-compose.yml) | 5-service deployment (DB, ETL, ML API, Dashboard, Chatbot) |
| 4× Dockerfiles | ETL, ML, Dashboard, Chatbot containers |

