## How to Run

```bash
# Navigate to project
cd C:\Users\mmmon\.gemini\antigravity\scratch\icc-t20-wc-predictor

# 1. Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# 2. Download datasets (downloads ~100MB+ from Cricsheet)
python src/ingestion/download_data.py

# 3. Run the full ETL pipeline
python src/etl/run_pipeline.py

# 4. Try the simulator (streams 5 matches to console)
python src/simulation/stream_simulator.py --interval 0.1
```

